authn.idp_settings.response_consumer_url.titl: URL for receipt of a response

authn.service_provider_id.description.titl: Service provider identifier, who figures as the party requesting user authentication. Typically a second class domain (e.g. tt>flexibee.eu).

authn.sso_cert_fingerprint.description.titl:
Here the SHA1 certificate stamp is entered, which will be used to sign responses. The correct format can be obtained, for example, via the command: openssl x509 -noout -in cert.pem -fingerprint -sha1
Leave empty if the certificate validation is not supposed to be done.

authn.sso_chng_passwd_url.description.titl: URL to which it will be possible to redirect users for the purpose of central logoff or change of password for the ID provider.

authn.sso_login_url.description.titl: URL to which ABRA Flexi (service) will send requests for user authentication. The request contains all necessary details for performing authentication, but it is often still necessary to create configuration on the ID provider’s side for the particular service. It is often necessary to specify the URL for processing a response and certain other parameters of the authentication protocol:

authn.type.GOOGLE.description.titl: Authorization is performed against Google servers. Both paid and free variants of Google Apps can be used.

authn.type.INTERNAL.description.titl: Only the name and password stored in ABRA Flexi is used.

authn.type.IT_HIGHWAY.description.titl: Authorization via a network of integrated services IT Highway.

authn.type.OPENID.description.titl: Authorization is performed against a regular OpenID provider. Configuration will need to be done.

authn.type.SAML.description.titl: Authorization is performed against a regular SAMLv2 Identity Provider. Configuration will need to be done.

devdoc.bezPolozek.titl: Does this document contain items? If it does, amount is determined by their sum. Otherwise, it is possible to set amount directly (sumCelkSniz etc.)

devdoc.datUhr.titl: Date of payment. Filled when the document was paid.

devdoc.faUlice.titl: Postal address. Fill in only if postovniShodna is false. If the item 'company' is filled in, it is not necessary to add additional information as the information will be copied form the address book.

devdoc.firma.titl: Link to company in directory. If not completed, then items should be completed with detailed information about the company.

devdoc.ic.titl: If the item 'company' is filled in, it is not necessary to add additional information as the information will be copied form the address book.

devdoc.kurz.titl: Rate, which is determines the conversion between the company's currency and the document currency. If the currency is not filled in, it has a zero value.

devdoc.kurzMnozstvi.titl: Exchange amount, which defines the relationship between the company's base currency and the document currency. E.g. the rate between the Czech crown and the Japanese yen is determined as CZK 1:  JPY 100.

devdoc.mesto.titl: If the item 'company' is filled in, it is not necessary to add additional information as the information will be copied form the address book.

devdoc.nazFirmy.titl: If the item 'company' is filled in, it is not necessary to add additional information as the information will be copied form the address book.

devdoc.postovniShodna.titl: If it is true, that postal address = invoice address. if the item 'company' is filled in, it is not necessary to add additional information as the information will be copied form the address book.

devdoc.psc.titl: If the item 'company' is filled in, it is not necessary to add additional information as the information will be copied form the address book.

devdoc.slevaDokl.titl: Total discount for document applied to resulting price.

devdoc.sumCelkSniz.titl: Total sum of all bases at the reduced VAT rate (i.e. amount not including VAT) in the company's base currency. If the document is itemised it is automatically figured from items.

devdoc.sumCelkSnizMen.titl: Total sum of all bases at the reduced VAT rate (i.e. amount not including VAT) in the document currency. If the currency of the document is identical to the company's base currency, this item is zero value. If the document is itemised it is automatically figured from items.

devdoc.sumCelkZakl.titl: Total sum of all bases a the basic rate of VAT (i.e. amount not including VAT) in the company's base currency. If the document is itemised it is automatically figured from items.

devdoc.sumCelkZaklMen.titl: Total sum of all bases at the basic VAT rate (i.e. amount not including VAT) in the document currency. If the currency of the document is identical to the company's base currency, this item is zero value. If the document is itemised it is automatically figured from items.

devdoc.sumCelkem.titl: Total sum including VAT in the company's base currency. (i.e. how much the customer should pay). If the document is itemised it is automatically figured from items.

devdoc.sumCelkemMen.titl: Total sum including VAT in the document currency. If the currency of the document is identical to the company's base currency, this item is zero value. (i.e. how much the customer should pay). If the document is itemised it is automatically figured from items.

devdoc.sumDphCelkem.titl: Total amount of VAT (sum of reduced and basic rate) in the company's base currency. If the document is itemised it is automatically figured from items.

devdoc.sumDphCelkemMen.titl: Total amount of VAT (sum of reduced and basic rate) in the document currency. If the currency of the document is identical to the company's base currency, this item is zero value. If the document is itemised it is automatically figured from items.

devdoc.sumDphSniz.titl: The total amount of VAT at a reduced rate of VAT in the company's base currency. If the document is itemised it is automatically figured from items.

devdoc.sumDphSnizMen.titl: The total amount of VAT at a reduced rate of VAT in the document currency. If the currency of the document is identical to the company's base currency, this item is zero value. If the document is itemised it is automatically figured from items.

devdoc.sumDphZakl.titl: Total amount of VAT at the basic rate in the company's base currency. If the document is itemised it is automatically figured from items.

devdoc.sumDphZaklMen.titl: The total amount of VAT at the basic rate of VAT in the document currency. If the currency of the document is identical to the company's base currency, this item is zero value. If the document is itemised it is automatically figured from items.

devdoc.sumOsv.titl: Total sum of bases exempt from VAT in the company's base currency. If the document is itemised it is automatically figured from items.

devdoc.sumOsvMen.titl: Total sum of bases exempt from VAT in the document currency. If the currency of the document is identical to the company's base currency, this item is zero value. If the document is itemised it is automatically figured from items.

devdoc.sumZklCelkem.titl: Total sum of all bases (i.e. amount not including VAT) in the company's base currency. This is the resulting amount not including VAT. If the document is itemised it is automatically figured from items.

devdoc.sumZklCelkemMen.titl: Total sum of all bases (i.e. amount not including VAT) in the document currency. If the currency of the document is identical to the company's base currency, this item is zero value. This is the resulting amount not including VAT. If the document is itemised it is automatically figured from items.

devdoc.sumZklSniz.titl: Total sum of bases with reduced VAT in the company's base currency. If the document is itemised it is automatically figured from items.

devdoc.sumZklSnizMen.titl: Total sum of bases with reduced VAT in the document currency. If the currency of the document is identical to the company's base currency, this item is zero value. If the document is itemised it is automatically figured from items.

devdoc.sumZklZakl.titl: Total sum of bases exempt from VAT in the company's base currency. If the document is itemised it is automatically figured from items.

devdoc.sumZklZaklMen.titl: Total sum of bases with basic VAT in the document currency. If the currency of the document is identical to the company's base currency, this item is zero value. If the document is itemised it is automatically figured from items.

root.explanation.titl: ABRA Flexi js a modern accounting and management system competent for the quality processing of accounting and related agendas for a broad spectrum of companies. Hidden behind an easy-to-use user interfaceis a robust and powerful client - server application that can be run on Windows, Linux and Mac OS X. Economic systems produced by ABRA Flexi been on the market since 1991
